## 3. Imbalances flagged

1. **Vertical pull is under-trained** (9 sets vs 15 vertical push, 0.6:1). Add 1 dedicated weighted pull-up day this coming week, and a chin-up accessory on a press day.
2. **Zero direct rear delt / upper-back work.** Add face pulls or band pull-aparts (10-15 reps) as a finisher 2x/wk — cheap insurance against pressing-heavy posture issues.
3. **Conditioning modality monoculture** (bike + carry only). Rotate in: row, ski, sled push, devil press, wall ball. Per `notes/0420-0425`: max 1 KB-swing day/wk.
4. **Strict press at the 1RM wall** (155# failed twice unprompted). Park 1RM attempts. Run 5×5 @ 70-78% (110-120#) for 3-4 weeks of accumulated volume before next test day.
5. **Bench top set stuck at 185#.** Repeat 185# 5×5 next bench day; only progress to 190# after a clean session.

